# ─── Antigravity Memory Sync — Ignore Rules ──────────────────
# Files matching these patterns will be SKIPPED during sync.
# Uses glob-style patterns. One pattern per line. Lines starting with # are comments.

# ── Browser screenshots & recordings (auto-generated, ~130MB) ──
*.webp
media__*.png
current_project_*.png
gcp_*.png
gcp_*.webp
google_drive_*.png
oauth_*.png
project_created_*.png
uploaded_media_*.png
github_actions_*.png
github_actions_*.webp

# ── System-generated logs (can be regenerated) ──
.system_generated/

# ── VS Code temp files ──
*.code-workspace

# ── Conflict backups (local only) ──
*.conflict.*

# ── Build artifacts ──
*.vsix
node_modules/
out/
